docs {
  ## Get Aggregate Attestation

  Aggregates all attestations matching given attestation data root and slot. A validator that is assigned to aggregate attestations calls this endpoint to collect an aggregate for broadcasting.

  ### Query Parameters
  - `attestation_data_root`: HashTreeRoot of the attestation data to aggregate (32-byte hex string).
  - `slot`: The slot for which the aggregate attestation is requested.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "aggregation_bits": "0xff3f",
      "data": {
        "slot": "1",
        "index": "0",
        "beacon_block_root": "0xcf8e0d4e9587369b2301d0790347320302cc0943d5a1884560367e8208d920f2",
        "source": {
          "epoch": "0",
          "root": "0x4b363db94e286120d76eb905340fcd4e979ae41e26b22f72b66852b3e8e3377b"
        },
        "target": {
          "epoch": "0",
          "root": "0xa1de6e671cdf96f52d35f9a0cd20b7ce38e1eb2db3a710f62aaf4036aaed7cb3"
        }
      },
      "signature": "0xb3a7e2c6f89a1b4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f70819"
    }
  }
  ```
}
